    <h2 class="wholesale-benefits__title">
      THAT'S WHY ZENGAZ IS DESIGNED NOT JUST AS A <span class="highlight">GREAT PRODUCT,</span> BUT ALSO AS A <span class="highlight">GREAT PARTNER,</span> MAKING YOUR BUSINESS <span class="highlight">EASIER</span> AND <span class="highlight">MORE PROFITABLE</span>
    </h2>
